Author: flortotheno
Text: You don't know how much that means, tysm. It was hell on earth, but it was possible. You'll get to recover too!

Author: glugglugbiggulp
Text: Hey, I just wanted to say that I read your post. And lifting your calories up all by yourself - god damn, you deserve all of my respect and I look up to you. You’re really strong. I’m trying to do the same, but I just gotta reach out to a dietician. The food related baggage is too heavy and I need someone to tell me face to face it’s okay to eat at maintenance and okay to eat simple carbs and stuff.
